OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBreezy start to Easter Sunday
OL,6,Fwith some bright spells. Turning
OL,7,Fcloudier for a time as occasional
OL,8,Fblustery showers move east, these
OL,9,Fbecoming isolated later with sunny
OL,10,Fspells developing into the early
OL,11,Fevening, and winds slowly easing.
OL,12,FFeeling cooler than Saturday.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FAny residual showers quickly
OL,15,Ffading to leave a dry night with long
OL,16,Fclear spells, and winds becoming
OL,17,Fgenerally light. Turning widely cold
OL,18,Fwith a slight frost developing in
OL,19,Fplaces.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
