OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FStarting chilly with a slight
OL,6,Ffrost in places. A dry day to follow
OL,7,Fwith variable cloud but also bright
OL,8,Fspells at times. Generally light
OL,9,Fwinds, with near average afternoon
OL,10,Ftemperatures.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FChilly
OL,13,Fstart Tuesday, then fine with warm
OL,14,Fsunshine and breezier, but cooler
OL,15,Fwhere any onshore winds. Very warm
OL,16,Fsunshine Wednesday, cloudier later.
OL,17,FThursday, cooler and breezy with
OL,18,Fsunshine and showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
